profile:
Xolar is a full service turn-key platform for transitioning residential clients to solar energy. We support our clients with our done-for-you approach, taking you all the way from project design to construction.  We have completed projects all over Ontario, and have many happy customers.  Our customer referral program allows your system to pay for itself in more ways than one.

Visit our website at www.xolar.ca
Check out our work on instagram @xolar.energy

Ottawa Solar Power is the largest and most experienced provider of solar solutions in the National Capital Region with over 500 grid-tied and off-grid systems installed. 

Ottawa Solar Power has a Better Business Bureau “A+” rating for Solar installations in the Ottawa area. 

Our focus on customer service has helped us grow our business steadily since 1996. We are trusted by commercial, institutional, and residential clients throughout the National Capital Region, and beyond.

profile:
iSolara Solar Power was formed in 2003 with the clear goal of providing well-installed, high quality renewable energy systems to reduce the effects of  Global Warming.

iSolara Solar Power is the leading solar System Integrator in Eastern Ontario. We serve residential and commercial customers from Belleville to the Quebec border.

To date we have sold & installed over 300 solar energy systems comprising 3 MW of clean renewable power generation.

Our vision is to enable every citizen, business and organization to invest in green energy solutions.


Our Values
we deliver premium value to our customers at a fair price
we stand by our values and meet our commitments
we expect to be fairly rewarded for our efforts
we are committed to innovation and the long term viability of this industry
we hire competent people with high integrity
